t\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"#top\">[^]</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr width=\"25%\" noshade align=\"center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p ALIGN=\"center\"><a name=\"chuong8\"></a><strong><font face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#000080\"><i>Chương \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTám</i></font></strong></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 ALIGN=\"center\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#000080\">Phẩm Pàtaligàmiya</font></h3>"
